title: Commission Regulation (EEC) No 374/92 of 17 February 1992 amending the Annex to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products
header:
COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 374/92  of 17 February 1992  amending the Annex to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products
THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
main_body:
In the Annex to Regulation (EEC) No 804/68, the following codes are added after CN code 2008 11 10:
CN code  Description     'ex 2008 92  "Muesli" type breakfast cereals containing unroasted cereal flakes  ex 2008 99  "Muesli" type breakfast cereals containing unroasted cereal flakes'

This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities.
It shall apply with effect from 1 January 1992. This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.
attachments:
Done at Brussels, 17 February 1992. For the Commission
Ray MAC SHARRY
Member of the Commission
